---
import Layout from '../../Base.astro';
import SimpleHero from '../../components/SimpleHero.astro';
import FeaturedArticles from "../../components/FeaturedArticles.astro";
import ServicesRelatedWork from "../../components/ServicesRelatedWork.astro";
import "../../styles/pages/_services-list.scss";

---

<Layout
	title='Digital Design | Graphic Design Agency from Brooksville Florida'
	description={`When your digital touchpoints feel disconnected, attention drops and conversions follow. We design digital experiences that are clear, useful, and built around the action you need people to take.`}
>
	<SimpleHero tagline='Branding & Design Services' title='Digital Design' description="When your digital touchpoints feel disconnected, attention drops and conversions follow. We design digital experiences that are clear, useful, and built around the action you need people to take." lottieFile="digital-design.json"/>
	<div class='service-body'>
		<div class='wrapper wrapper--narrow'>
			<h2>Where teams get stuck</h2>
			<p>Businesses often end up with landing pages, emails, product screens, and marketing assets that all feel like they came from different places. That inconsistency makes the experience harder to trust and harder to use.</p>
			<p>When visitors have to work too hard to understand what they are looking at, attention fades before action happens.</p>
			<h2>How we fix it</h2>
			<p>We design digital experiences with hierarchy, usability, and brand consistency in mind so people can quickly understand what matters and what to do next.</p>
			<ul>
				<li>Web design</li>
				<li>Landing page design</li>
				<li>App design</li>
				<li>Infographic design</li>
				<li>Email design</li>
			</ul>
			<h2>What moving forward looks like</h2>
			<p>If you need a new digital touchpoint or an existing one cleaned up, we can map the user flow, prioritize the content, and design something your team can confidently build and maintain.</p>
			<p><a href='/contact/' class='button button--green'>Talk Through Your Design Project</a></p>
		</div>
		<ServicesRelatedWork tag={74} />
	</div>
	<FeaturedArticles />
</Layout>
